This is the default [[sound sequence]] for closing a normal door with a DORW* (but not DORWL*) texture in ''[[Strife]]''. It is redirected from [[DoorSmallWood]].
==== [[SNDSEQ]] definition ==== :DoorCloseSmallWood play doors/small_wood_close nostopcutoff end [[Category:Sound sequences]]
